---
layout: layouts/component-demo.njk
title: Datetime Local Input
description: an input for entering a date and time without time zone
---

{% from "components/date-time-local-input/macro.njk" import datetimeLocalInput %}
{% from "components/label/macro.njk" import label %}
{% from "components/hint/macro.njk" import hint %}
{% from "components/field/macro.njk" import field %}

<h2>Appointment booking</h2>
{% call field() %}
  {{ label({ for: "appt", text: "Preferred date and time" }) }}
  {{ hint({
    id: "appt-hint",
    text: "Choose a slot between 9am and 5pm, weekdays only."
  }) }}
  {{ datetimeLocalInput({
    id: "appt",
    describedBy: "appt-hint",
    min: "2026-04-20T09:00",
    max: "2026-07-31T17:00",
    step: 900,
    value: "2026-04-27T09:30"
  }) }}
{% endcall %}

<p>The value format is <code>YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM</code> without
  time-zone offset. If your application is multi-zone, store the
  submitted value with an explicit time zone at the server.</p>
